page.title: 01EYKE PARISH: General View
page.content:
This is an area consisting of heath- land, now largely over planted with coniferous woodland by the Forestry Commission. There is one ancient wood- land. A small area is cultivated wood- land.
There are three small hamlets; Friday Street, which is just within the Rendlesham boundary, the Rookery Estate and Spratt Street.
